description:
Guest artist, Bobby McFerrin, answers a question from the audience at Berklee College of Music about his influence on the beat boxing world. 

For the full story and more great posts, visit Berklee-Blogs.com!
fulltitle: Bobby McFerrin on His Influence on the Beat Boxing World
